This is a sudoku solver and generator with a user interface 
written using the gtkmm-library.

The software runs under Linux (i just tried Ubuntu) and Windows using
the MSVC-compiler.

Building:

Linux-Systems 

- the cmake build system is required
- the gtkmm development packages are required
- pkgconfig is required
 
Windows Systems

You can build the sudoku programs using the Visual Studio 2005 and 2008.

- Download and install gtkmm at http://live.gnome.org/gtkmm/MSWindows
- Build the application using the following the guidelines at
http://live.gnome.org/gtkmm/MSWindows#gtkmm_on_Microsoft_Windows 

